>.<

Title: Highest Salary & Full Name
Link: https://platform.stratascratch.com/coding/9866-highest-salary-and-full-name?code_type=3
Level: Easy

Your output should include the full name of the employee(s) with the highest salary in one column and the corresponding salary in the other.

Data worker:
department: text
first_name: text
joining_date: datetime
last_name: text
salary: bigint
worker_id: bigint

>.<

Solution:

select concat(first_name,last_name) fullname,max(salary) highest_salary
from worker;
    
Output:

fullname    |  highest_salary
MonikaArora        500000
